{"title": "荣格自传：梦、记忆和思考", "index": 37, "content": [{"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_6b04e6bb9f.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "图书在版编目（CIP）数据"}, {"type": "text", "value": "荣格自传：梦、记忆和思考/（瑞士）荣格著；高鸣译．—南昌：江西人民出版社，2014.10"}, {"type": "text", "value": "ISBN 978-7-210-06714-6"}, {"type": "text", "value": "Ⅰ．①荣…　Ⅱ．①荣…②高…　Ⅲ．①荣格，C．G．（1875~1961）—自传　Ⅳ．①K835.226.2"}, {"type": "text", "value": "中国版本图书馆CIP数据核字（2014）第213856号"}, {"type": "text", "value": "荣格自传：梦、记忆和思考"}, {"type": "text", "value": "（瑞士）卡尔·古斯塔夫·荣格　著　高鸣　译"}, {"type": "text", "value": "江西人民出版社出版发行"}, {"type": "text", "value": "地址：江西省南昌市三经路47号附1号（邮编：330006）"}, {"type": "text", "value": "编辑部电话：0791-86898980"}, {"type": "text", "value": "发行部电话：0791-86898801"}, {"type": "text", "value": "网址：www.jxpph.com"}, {"type": "text", "value": "E-mail：jxpph@tom.com　web@jxpph.com"}, {"type": "text", "value": "2014年12月第1版　2014年12月第1次印刷"}, {"type": "text", "value": "开本：170毫米×240毫米　1/16"}, {"type": "text", "value": "印张：20.5　插页：8"}, {"type": "text", "value": "字数：330千字"}, {"type": "text", "value": "ISBN 978-7-210-06714-6"}, {"type": "text", "value": "赣版权登字—01—2014—511"}, {"type": "text", "value": "版权所有　侵权必究"}, {"type": "text", "value": "定价：39.80元"}, {"type": "text", "value": "承印厂：北京画中画印刷有限公司"}, {"type": "text", "value": "赣人版图书凡属印刷、装订错误，请随时向承印厂调换"}, {"type": "text", "value": "目录"}, {"type": "text", "value": "序言"}, {"type": "text", "value": "一、童年时光"}, {"type": "text", "value": "二、中学岁月"}, {"type": "text", "value": "三、大学年代"}, {"type": "text", "value": "四、精神病治疗活动"}, {"type": "text", "value": "五、西格蒙德·弗洛伊德"}, {"type": "text", "value": "六、直面潜意识"}, {"type": "text", "value": "七、著作"}, {"type": "text", "value": "八、塔楼生活"}, {"type": "text", "value": "九、游途"}, {"type": "text", "value": "Ⅰ　北非"}, {"type": "text", "value": "Ⅱ　美国：贝勃罗印第安人"}, {"type": "text", "value": "Ⅲ　肯尼亚和乌干达"}, {"type": "text", "value": "Ⅳ　印度"}, {"type": "text", "value": "Ⅴ　拉文纳与罗马"}, {"type": "text", "value": "十、幻象"}, {"type": "text", "value": "十一、死后生活"}, {"type": "text", "value": "十二、后期思想"}, {"type": "text", "value": "十三、我的一生"}, {"type": "text", "value": "返回总目录"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_617620d0b7.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "童年时期的荣格"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_595868541e.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "少年时期的荣格"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_75a040b323.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "荣格的父母"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_8e8a53dfde.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "青年时期的荣格、妹妹与父母在一起"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_a5d9921755.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "年轻时的荣格和妻子爱玛"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_d9fcd83e62.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1906年，弗洛伊德和荣格在家庆祝荣格生日"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_7c8e5d438d.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "弗洛伊德与荣格1909年访美时合影，弗洛伊德（左）、霍尔（中）、荣格（右），后面站着的是弗洛伊德的学生"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_e20d75229a.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "弗洛伊德和荣格在莱茵河附近的海岸钓鱼"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_1bb1faa8b0.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "荣格，1910年"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_03035e1a90.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "参加马塞诸萨州伍斯特市心理学会议的相关人员合影，前排右三为荣格"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_e8f3b03374.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "荣格夫妇与弗洛伊德夫妇一起休假"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_b3835d253c.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "斯宾娜·史毕莱，荣格的情人与启发者，精神分析运动的重要人物，同时也是该领域极其罕见的女性，其思想和工作极大地影响了荣格与弗洛伊德的理论，很多人认为荣格所说的阿尼玛即是受斯宾娜的启发而来"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_696ab9a496.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "阿尼玛和阿尼姆斯"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_7c1c85aadb.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "波林根的石刻，中间是提灯人"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_d336a0fafd.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "荣格会见朋友"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_cf01383684.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "荣格一家：（右起）二女儿安娜、三女儿玛利娅、大女儿阿卡莎、儿子费郎兹（2）"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_5945014024.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "晚年的荣格与妻子爱玛，艾玛不但是荣格的妻子，也是荣格最忠实的助手"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_863a53b8b9.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "荣格在塔楼里阅读，这个房间是属于他个人的空间"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_63362916da.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1936年，荣格在艾诺思听马森·奥瑟尔作关于印度哲学的报告"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_f5cf6e1492.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "荣格在波林根的塔楼，那里直到现在也没有任何现代化电器设备"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_ca9d72b088.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "隐居在波林根的荣格过着朴实的乡村生活"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_54c10ce9d6.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1960年，荣格家族全家福。其时，荣格已届85岁高龄"}]}